<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.8">
<l>vāḷai yārtaṭan kaṇṇumai paṅkaṉvaṉ cāpamaṟ ṟatunīṅka</l>
<l>mūḷai yārcirat taiyamu ṉaḷittavem mukilvaṇṇa ṉuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>pāḷai vāṉkamu kūṭuyar teṅkiṉvaṉ paḻamviḻa veruvippōy</l>
<l>vāḷai pāytaṭañ cūḻtaru nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells our cloud-colored one who once gave alms</l>
<l rend="indent">in a brain-filled skull</l>
<l>To remove it, ending the harsh curse on him whose one half is Umā,</l>
<l rend="indent">with vāḷai [fish]-like, wide eyes,</l>
<l>Is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr which is surrounded by ponds</l>
<l rend="indent">where vāḷai [fish] leap, fleeing,</l>
<l>Fearing as large fruit of tall coconut [palms] fall between</l>
<l rend="indent">the large arecas with bracts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
